1)Display the information details of employee whose designation is MANAGER/manager
A)  grep -i "MANAGER" DETAILS.csv
2)Display whose name starts with the letter c/C
A) cut -d, -f 1 DETAILS.csv| grep -i "c"
3)Replace Manager with Director in the "Designation" field
A) sed 's/MANAGER/DIRECTOR/g' DETAILS.csv
4)Allow a search for different formats in a name [for example, Kishan]
A) grep -e "VIJAYALAKSHMI" -e "KISHAN" -e "KISHAN" DETAILS.txt

